quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  38,84,"Allah daali: goonga kan ko e Am, ko goonga Mi wowlata, wanaa ko lunndi …óum."
  38,85,"Ma Mi hebbinire Jahannama √ëande Darngal, an e …ìen jokku…ìe ma, yeddu…ìe …ìen e banii Aadama …ìen fow."
  38,86,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan sirkoo…ìe …ìen: Mi lamndaaki on e ko mi yottinta e mon kon, njo…ìdi. Mi wonaali kadi etotoo…óo sincugol …ìeyda e ko mi yamiraa kon."
  38,87,"Alqur'aana wonaali, si wanaa waaju, wonannde hellifaa…ìe yim…ìe e jinna …ìen."
  38,88,"Ma on anndu kabaaru ndee Alqur'aanaare, wonnde ko nde goonga, …ìaawo dummunna …ìadii…óo, tuma nde maayoton."
  39,1,"Jippagol Alqur'aana, ko immorde ka Allah, Foolu…óo Mo gooto foolataa, √ëee√±u…óo e tagu Mun, e toppitagol Mun e sari'a Mun. Wanaa e go…ó…óo goo, ko woori Mo, nde jippori."
  39,2,"Men jippinirii Deftere Alqur'aana nden e maa…óa, an Nulaa…óo, e hoore goonga. Kumpite mayre fow ko goonga, √±aawooje mayre fow kadi ko nun…óu…óe. Haray rewu Allah, wootin…óinaa mo, la…ì…ìinanaa Mo tawhiidi e hoore sirku."
  39,3,"Anndee, ko Allah woodani, diina laa…ìuka e sirku kan. ∆Åen non …ìe …ìeya jogitori yi…ó…ìe gaanin Allah, immorde e sanamuuji e bewinay…ói, …ói …ìe rewata …ìe acca Allah, …ìe wona e ngantinorgol …óum, wiide: Men rewiraali …óii, si wanaa tun no …ìadinira men ka Allah, martaba, …ói hewtina Mo haajuuji amen, …ói tefana men ka Makko. Pellet, Allah √±aawoyay hakkunde gom…óim…ìe wootim…ìe Mo …ìen, e yeddu…ìe sirku…ìe …ìen, √ëalnde Darngal, e kon ko …ìe luutondiraynoo e mun, ka tawhiidi. Pellet, Allah fewnataa e goonga, on fenoowo dammba e Alla sirku, dullanoowo neemaaji Allah …óin e makko."
  39,4,"Sinno Allah yi…óuo siforgol …ìi…ó…óo, O su…ìotono ko O yi…ói, e tagu Makko ngun, O wa…óa on …óon …ìi…ó…óo Makko. Kono O senike O laa…ìii e kon ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen wowolata ! Ko Kanko woni Allah Gooto On ka jaati, e ka sijaafi e ka golle Makko. Kafidii…óo alanaa Mo e …óin. Ko O Foolu…óo tagu Makko ngun fow."
  39,5,"O tagirii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, √±en∆¥al yottiingal, ko fijindaaru alaa e mu'un, wano too√±u…ìe …ìen aa∆¥orta. Himo suddira jemma on, √±alawma on, O suddira kadi √±alorma on, jemma on. O elti naange ngen e lewru ndun, tawi kala majji, hino doga haa e happu e…ì…ìaa…óo, on woni lannugol …óam nguurndam. Haray anndee, ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, yoftotoowo ay…ìe Mun, Mo gooto foolataa, Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."